message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product for $120. I think it's a great deal for something of this quality.
Hi Alice, thank you for your offer. I appreciate the quality of the product, but I am only willing to pay $95. I hope we can come to an agreement.
Thanks for the offer, Bob. I understand your budget, but I can't go lower than $110. This product is truly worth it.
Hello Alice, I appreciate your response. Considering my budget constraints, I would like to propose a price of $100 for the product. I believe this is a fair compromise given its value.
